  ('dietitian-moex-10616', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-094-cd594556', 'sub-dietitian-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '胰蛋白 （Trypsin）之催化胜 鍵（peptide bond）水解斷裂的特性，下列敘述何者為真？ 催化水解Arginine和Tryptophan之C-peptide bonds 催化水解Lysine和Tyrosine之N-peptide bonds 催化水解Aliphatic amino acid之C-peptide bonds 催化水解Lysine和Arginine之C-peptide bonds', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:56+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "de86e5e3c8c3", "answer_pdf_sha1": "794bf55cd1a4", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "094020", "c": "112", "s": "2001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "營養學", "year": "094", "exam_name": "094年第一次專技醫事人員、中醫師、心理師、呼吸治療師、營養師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 1, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-10617', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-094-cd594556', 'sub-dietitian-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '胺基酸之吸收可因某些抗生素而受抑制，其可能作用機制為： 干擾其stereo-specific membrane bound transport system之結構 與unnatural D-isomer chelating而抑制其吸收 抑制transport protein之synthesis 造成腸道的鹼性環境，影響胺基酸之溶解性', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:56+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "de86e5e3c8c3", "answer_pdf_sha1": "794bf55cd1a4", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "094020", "c": "112", "s": "2001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "營養學", "year": "094", "exam_name": "094年第一次專技醫事人員、中醫師、心理師、呼吸治療師、營養師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 2, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
